{"lemma":"أَوْبَرِ","slug":"أَوْبَرِ","root":"#.ب.ر","root_slug":"_-ب-ر","root_link":"/words/roots/_-ب-ر","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":false},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n41565"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%A3%D9%8E%D9%88%D9%92%D8%A8%D9%8E%D8%B1%D9%90"}},"translations":null,"definition":null,"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n41565","headword_ar":"اَوْبَرُ","root":"wbr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wabirN","text_ar":"وَبِرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"banaAtu A^awobara","text_ar":"بَنَاتُ اَوْبَرَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (As, A 'Obeyd, AHn, T, S, M, K,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"banaAtu AlA^awobari","text_ar":"بَنَاتُ الاَوْبَرِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (AZ, T, S, M,) the art. being added by poetic license, (M,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A species of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kamoA^ap","text_ar":"كَمْاَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"truffles"},{"kind":"text","text":"],"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"downy,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(AZ, As, A 'Obeyd, T, S, M, [the epithet thus rendered is written in copies of the K"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"muzogibapN","text_ar":"مُزْغِبَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and in the T, S, M,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"muzag~ibapN","text_ar":"مُزَغِّبَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", but in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zgb","text_ar":"زغب"},{"kind":"text","text":"in the TA it seems to be indicated that it is probably"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"muzogib~apN","text_ar":"مُزْغِبَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":",])"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"small, and of the colour of earth:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(AZ, S, K:) or,"},{"kind":"page_break","n":2916},{"kind":"text","text":"accord. to AHn,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"truffles"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kmA^p","text_ar":"كماة"},{"kind":"text","text":")"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"like pebbles, small, found in places where they have broken through the crust of the soil, in number from one to ten; they are bad in flavour; and are the first of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kmA^p","text_ar":"كماة"},{"kind":"text","text":": or, as he says in another place,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"they are like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kmA^p","text_ar":"كماة"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"but are not"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kmA^p","text_ar":"كماة"},{"kind":"text","text":";"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and they are small:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M: see also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jabo'N","text_ar":"جَبْءٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":":]) n. un."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_ibonu A^awobara","text_ar":"اـِبْنُ اَوْبَرَ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (As, A 'Obeyd, T.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_in~a baniY fulaAnK mivolu","text_ar":"اـِنَّ بَنِى فُلَانٍ مِثْلُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"banaAti A^awobara","text_ar":"بَنَاتِ اَوْبَرَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Verily the sons of such a one are like benát-owbar"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: one imagines that there is good in them [when there is none]. (M.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laqiytu","text_ar":"لَقِيتُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"manohu banaAta A^awobara","text_ar":"مَنْهُ بَنَاتَ اَوْبَرَ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I experienced from him"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a disappointment,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a calamity,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"misfortune."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Sgh, K.) ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"daAhiyapN waboraA='u","text_ar":"دَاهِيَةٌ وَبْرَا=ءُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, A, art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$Er","text_ar":"شعر"},{"kind":"text","text":"), (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"An evil, a foul,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an abominable, calamity,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"misfortune."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA, voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^a$oEaru","text_ar":"اَشْعَرُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", q. v.)"}],"source_refs":["AZ","T","S","M","K"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}